high_descs: Turn and go to the center counter.
Pick up the pan on the counter.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn and go to the cabinet by the stove.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed pan in the cabinet by the stove.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step to your left then walk past the counter on your right then turn right and walk a step then turn right to face the middle of that side of the counter.
Pick up the dirty frying pan that's in front of you.
Turn left and take a step to your left then walk to the sink.
Wash the dirty pan in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and take a step to your left then take a step backwards so you can use the cupboard to the right of the stove.
Open the cupboards down to the right of the stove and put the clean frying pan under there before closing the doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean frying pan in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around and take one step, then turn right and take three steps, then turn right and take two steps, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the pan in the middle of the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the pan in the sink then turn the water on for three seconds, then turn the water off and pick up the pan.
Turn around and take one step, then turn to the right and open the cabinet to the right of the stove.
Put the pan in the cabinet to the right of the stove.
